              >• 1</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.01em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >scenario book &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9333em; top: 22.8796em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.2419em"
              >• </span
            ><span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_100" style="word-spacing: 0.0435em"
              >Fortresses: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0498em"
              >A </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_23" style="word-spacing: 0.1051em"
              >fortress </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0949em"
              >is a fortified space represented by an &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5998em; top: 23.8296em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_88" style="word-spacing: -0.0108em"
              >eight-pointed star. Fortresses are walled towns with little eco-
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5998em; top: 24.7796em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.036em"
              >nomic value. In most cases they will not grant a power victory
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5998em; top: 25.7296em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_101" style="word-spacing: -0.0076em"
              >points. However, a fortress’s strong defenses force a power to
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5998em; top: 26.6796em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0619em"
              >besiege the space to gain political control. Powers may con-
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5998em; top: 27.6296em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0437em"
              >struct fortresses on simple unfortified spaces or in Exploration
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5998em; top: 28.5796em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >Map settlements. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.8916em; top: 23.1996em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.2419em"
              >• 6</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.01em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0002em"
              >sheets of counters &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.8916em; top: 24.3167em">
