              >• 4</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.01em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >Reference cards (identical, two-sided) &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.8916em; top: 29.9019em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.2419em"
              >• 1</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.01em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >Minor Power Diplomacy chart &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.8916em; top: 31.0189em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.2419em"
              >• 1</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.01em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_90" style="word-spacing: -0.0014em"
