              >action in a Portuguese home space). &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9167em; top: 5.5436em">
            <span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_268" style="word-spacing: 0.2519em"
              >• FOURTH</span
            ><span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.0538em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_61" style="word-spacing: -0.0699em"
              >PLACE: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_186" style="word-spacing: -0.0627em"
              >Do </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_61" style="word-spacing: -0.0658em"
              >not </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_79" style="word-spacing: -0.0631em"
              >execute your selected event. How- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5825em; top: 6.4936em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_97" style="word-spacing: -0.0371em"
              >ever, you may move any player’s influence marker on a Minor
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5825em; top: 7.4436em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_182" style="word-spacing: -0.0629em"
