            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.035em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0401em"
              >arriving in a Sea Zone containing units controlled by the ac-
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 44.1738em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0159em"
              >tive major power: the arriving naval unit(s) are placed on top
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 45.1238em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0031em"
              >of the other friendly units and oriented the same way as those
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 46.0738em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13">units. &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4166em; top: 47.2739em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2319em"
              >• If</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.029em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0341em"
              >arriving in a Sea Zone with no units controlled by the active
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 48.2239em">
