              >the winner. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 8.6934em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0749em"
              >Naval squadrons may be redeployed to an Ocean Zone to act as
