            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_30" style="word-spacing: 0.019em"
              >does this or it is Spain with another Nao, it will gain 1 VP for
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 27.5835em; top: 9.4412em; z-index: 2528"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.0182em"
