              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 11.877em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0058em"
              >settlements cannot be moved later in the game, although they
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 12.827em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >may occasionally be lost due to events. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 10.7283em">
            <span class="stl_10 stl_08 stl_404" style="word-spacing: 0.0292em"
              >Vasco da Gama’s Nao: &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 30.3947em; top: 13.4284em; z-index: 2560"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_194">V</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_99">a</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_89" style="word-spacing: 0.1114em"
