            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102">S</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_131" style="word-spacing: 0.0902em"
              >ettlement </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102">S</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.0909em"
              >urrenders </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.073em"
              >or </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_99">W</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_131" style="word-spacing: 0.0901em"
              >ithout </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102">P</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13">revious &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 5.0833em; top: 17.8271em; z-index: 661"
          >
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102">D</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_99">eclar</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_190">a</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13">t</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0043em"
              >ion </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.004em"
              >event is played against a Portuguese settlement &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 18.7771em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_170" style="word-spacing: -0.0648em"
              >in one of these spaces. Whenever the Portuguese player is creat-
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 19.7271em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_109" style="word-spacing: -0.0621em"
              >ing a new settlement in a zone with empty reserved Portuguese
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 20.6771em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_62" style="word-spacing: -0.0629em"
              >spaces (but remember the limitations of Turns 1 and 2), he must
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 21.6271em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0em"
