            style="left: 26.9169em; top: 15.995em; z-index: 2615"
          >
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102" style="word-spacing: 0.2322em"
              >• On</span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.0158em"
