            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_99">a</span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_123" style="word-spacing: 0.0013em"
              >sco da Gama’s first attempt to explore </span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_99">z</span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.003em"
