          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9169em; top: 19.1997em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18">•</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9358em; top: 19.2em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_79" style="word-spacing: -0.0621em"
              >If Portugal becomes the first player to found a settle</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_79" style="word-spacing: -0.0621em"
              >- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 30.9381em; top: 20.15em; z-index: 2795"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0217em"
              >ment in Zone 5 using </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_194">V</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_99">a</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_50" style="word-spacing: -0.0112em"
              >sco da Gama’s Nao, Portu- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 30.9381em; top: 21.1em; z-index: 2828"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_333" style="word-spacing: 0.1189em"
              >gal earns 2 V</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_405">P</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.153em"
              >. </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_406">G</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_245" style="word-spacing: 0.125em"
              >ive them the </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_333" style="word-spacing: 0.1248em"
              >Overseas </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_407">V</span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_333">o</span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_245">yage &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 27.5831em; top: 22.05em; z-index: 2874"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0451em"
              >marker (representing </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_194">V</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_99">a</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_101" style="word-spacing: -0.0315em"
              >sco da Gama’s arrival in India). If it is &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5831em; top: 23em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0581em"
              >another power that does this or it is Portugal with another Nao,
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 27.5831em; top: 23.95em; z-index: 2986"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0104em"
              >it will gain 1 VP for Overseas </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_393">V</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13">o</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0em"
              >yage instead. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01 stl_75" style="left: 3.75em; top: 23.3636em">
            <span class="stl_76 stl_08 stl_68" style="word-spacing: -0.0012em"
              >16.7 Special Exploration Events &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 24.9434em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_146" style="word-spacing: 0.1249em"
              >Three special event cards control the pace of Exploration Map
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 3.75em; top: 25.8934em; z-index: 1012"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_100" style="word-spacing: 0.0036em"
              >discoveries, as detailed in the sections below. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 26.25em; top: 25.2372em; z-index: 2999"
          >
