            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01 stl_75" style="left: 26.25em; top: 4.055em">
            <span class="stl_198 stl_08 stl_162" style="word-spacing: -0.031em"
              >18. Winter Phase &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 6.5528em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_109" style="word-spacing: 0.0244em"
              >The fifth phase of each turn is the Winter Phase, which starts
              im</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_109" style="word-spacing: 0.0244em"
              >- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 7.5028em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0515em"
              >mediately after the last impulse of the Action Phase. During this
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 8.4528em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0002em"
              >phase, all players complete the following actions in this order:
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01 stl_75" style="left: 3.75em; top: 8.9302em">
            <span class="stl_76 stl_08 stl_164" style="word-spacing: 0.005em"
