            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 9.653em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2318em"
              >• Resolve</span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0271em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0213em"
              >specific Mandatory Events if they have not occurred &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 10.603em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0em"
              >by their “due date” (18.1). &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 7.909em; top: 10.5101em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_84" style="word-spacing: 0.0676em"
              >Starting on Turn 3, all powers may spend 2 CPs on &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 7.905em; top: 11.4601em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0051em"
              >the Build Nao action. Randomly draw a Nao counter &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 7.905em; top: 12.4101em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.063em"
              >from your force pool and add it to the map in the Built
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 7.905em; top: 13.3601em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >Naos box on the undamaged (front) side. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 11.8032em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.2317em"
              >• Check</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.0181em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0231em"
              >for Military Order activity against corsairs and the loss
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 12.7532em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0em"
              >of Nasrid home spaces (18.2). &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 13.9533em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2319em"
              >• Discard</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.005em"
