          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 26.1545em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2318em"
              >• Reset</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.0579em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0632em"
              >the diplomatic status of minors resolved this turn to their
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 27.1045em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0002em"
              >starting levels (18.10). &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4167em; top: 27.094em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2319em"
              >• If</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.067em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.0619em"
              >you have two Naos on the Exploration Map, you may not
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 28.044em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.044em"
              >move another one from the Built Naos box to the map (zone
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 28.994em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0341em"
              >1) unless you voluntarily remove one of your other Naos from
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 29.944em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0em"
              >the map. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 28.4709em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_39" style="word-spacing: -0.0614em"
              >Each of these actions from the Winter Phase can be done
              simultane- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 29.4209em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >ously by all players to speed up the game. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4167em; top: 31.1441em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.2317em"
              >• When</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0219em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0169em"
              >a Nao is removed from the map for any reason, placed &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 32.0941em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_127" style="word-spacing: 0.0632em"
              >it on the next turn of the Turn Track. During the Card Draw
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 33.0441em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0431em"
              >Phase (8.1) these eliminated Nao units are returned to the pool
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 5.0833em; top: 33.9941em; z-index: 1251"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_144" style="word-spacing: 0.0029em"
              >of Naos units available to be constructed by that power.
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01 stl_75" style="left: 26.25em; top: 31.1563em">
            <span class="stl_76 stl_08 stl_101" style="word-spacing: -0.0055em"
              >18.1 Mandatory Events &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.2088em; top: 32.7362em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_330" style="word-spacing: 0.1249em"
              >The following events must occur by a &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.2088em; top: 33.6862em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_121" style="word-spacing: 0.1244em"
              >specified “due date”. If it is the Winter &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.2088em; top: 34.6362em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0361em"
              >Phase of the indicated turn and that event &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.2088em; top: 35.5862em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_245" style="word-spacing: 0.1249em"
              >has not yet been triggered, resolve the &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.2088em; top: 36.5362em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0178em"
              >event at this time, in the order indicated. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.2088em; top: 37.4862em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0609em"
              >The card is extracted from the deck and &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.2088em; top: 38.4362em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_235" style="word-spacing: -0.0622em"
              >removed from play as if it had been played &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.2088em; top: 39.3862em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0298em"
              >by one of the powers. The 3 CP normally &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.2088em; top: 40.3362em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.1229em"
              >granted to the power playing such card &nbsp;</span
            >
