            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 11.3942em">
            <span class="stl_10 stl_08 stl_164">Note: &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4167em; top: 12.6404em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2319em"
              >• If</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.043em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0379em"
              >the Spanish player controls all the Canary Islands they are
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 5.0833em; top: 13.5904em; z-index: 485"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_61" style="word-spacing: 0.0061em"
              >never subject to Plunder. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 13.1127em">
            <span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_458" style="word-spacing: 0.0317em"
              >MESTA: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >Spain now checks for trade results from the Mesta. The
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 14.0627em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0109em"
              >Spanish player receives a +1 die roll modifier for each port
              under &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 15.0127em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.023em"
              >Spanish control in the Cantabrian Sea to which the Spanish player
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 15.9627em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_107" style="word-spacing: -0.0631em"
              >can trace LoC from the Mesta marker (this LoC cannot pass through
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 16.9127em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_100" style="word-spacing: -0.011em"
              >another port in the Cantabrian Sea). If a Foreign War against
              Brit- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 17.8627em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0021em"
              >tany is active Spain rolls twice on the table. Roll two dice and
              the &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 18.8127em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_88" style="word-spacing: 0.0022em"
              >received resources are immediately added to Spain’s warehouse:
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4167em; top: 14.7905em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2318em"
              >• Plunder</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.076em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0709em"
              >of naval resources is mandatory and independent of &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0833em; top: 15.7405em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_109" style="word-spacing: -0.0591em"
              >whether the plundering power is at war, allied, or at peace with
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 5.0833em; top: 16.6905em; z-index: 604"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_21" style="word-spacing: 0.0122em"
              >the target power. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4167em; top: 17.8907em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.2419em"
              >• A</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0498em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0949em"
              >player who has played the </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_99">E</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.094em"
              >xperienced </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102">P</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0949em"
              >ilot </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.095em"
              >event this &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 5.0833em; top: 18.8407em; z-index: 678"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_293" style="word-spacing: 0.0054em"
