            ><span
              class="stl_208 stl_17 stl_422"
              style="word-spacing: -0.1162em"
              >EXAMPLE: </span
            ><span class="stl_209 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0539em"
              >Manuel I cannot marry Isabella while Afonso &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 57.8515em">
            <span class="stl_209 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0319em"
              >of Portugal is alive.) </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0267em"
              >Each CP spent represents an increase in the &nbsp;</span
            >
