              >sections below. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 41.788em">
            <span class="stl_10 stl_08 stl_30" style="word-spacing: -0.0002em"
              >Reconquest of the Nasrid Kingdom of Granada &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.7083em; top: 43.4165em">
            <span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_479" style="word-spacing: 0.0909em"
              >HISTORICAL NOTE: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_480" style="word-spacing: 0.1251em"
              >The war against the Kingdom of &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.7083em; top: 44.3665em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.03em"
