            ><span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_155">L</span
            ><span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_67">N</span
            ><span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_35" style="word-spacing: -0.0801em"
              >OTE: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_171" style="word-spacing: -0.0619em"
              >The Nasrid Kingdom lost control of the &nbsp;</span
            >
