            ><span class="stl_512 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0421em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_512 stl_17 stl_30" style="word-spacing: 0.0418em"
              >may build up to three Naos each turn instead of only &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01 stl_464" style="left: 5.0836em; top: 37.557em">
            <span class="stl_512 stl_17 stl_18">two. &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4167em; top: 38.757em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2319em"
              >• Portugal</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.0149em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0201em"
              >may move into and explore Ocean Zones 1, 2, and 3. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 39.2943em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18">•</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9169em; top: 47.1444em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18">•</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9457em; top: 39.2942em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_79" style="word-spacing: -0.062em"
              >The normal state of war between Portugal and Spain &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9583em; top: 40.2442em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0929em"
              >ends. Peace lasts at least for the remainder of the &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9583em; top: 41.1942em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0739em"
              >turn in which it is signed and one additional turn. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4167em; top: 39.9572em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2319em"
              >• Portugal</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.0389em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0442em"
              >may build settlements in any space in Zones 1, 2, and
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 5.0833em; top: 40.9072em; z-index: 1619"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_144" style="word-spacing: 0.0027em"
              >3; they are not limited to only spaces marked by their color.
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9583em; top: 42.1442em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0159em"
              >During this time Portugal and Spain may not go to &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 42.1942em">
            <span class="stl_10 stl_08 stl_27" style="word-spacing: -0.0013em"
              >Portugal´s Keys &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5835em; top: 43.0942em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_49" style="word-spacing: 0.0212em"
              >war. Place the </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_128" style="word-spacing: 0.0151em"
              >Alcaçovas in Force T1 </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0098em"
              >marker in its box in the &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5835em; top: 44.0442em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0157em"
              >Diplomatic Status Display as a reminder; flip it at the start of
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5835em; top: 44.9942em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_162" style="word-spacing: 0.0425em"
              >the second turn—and then remove it at the end of Turn 2 (to
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5835em; top: 45.9442em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0002em"
              >indicate your obligation to maintain it has expired).
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 43.4404em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.063em"
              >If two or more Portuguese home keys are not controlled by
              Portugal &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 44.3904em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_121" style="word-spacing: 0.1119em"
              >in the Card Draw Phase, subtract 1 from the Portuguese ruler’s
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 45.3404em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0471em"
              >charisma, placing a </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_179" style="word-spacing: -0.0289em"
              >–1 Card </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0471em"
              >marker on his Player Card that he will &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 46.2904em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >keep until he regains control again. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9131em; top: 47.1442em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_403">A</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_69">s</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_107" style="word-spacing: -0.0621em"
              >tate of war still exists between Portugal and Spain &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9582em; top: 48.0942em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.004em"
              >at sea. Place the </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_252">W</span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_13">a</span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0041em"
              >r at Sea </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0225em"
              >marker on the Alliance &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9582em; top: 49.0442em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_513" style="word-spacing: -0.0616em"
              >and War Table. Their naval squadrons intercept each &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9582em; top: 49.9942em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0432em"
              >other normally and either power may initiate piracy &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5834em; top: 50.9442em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_85" style="word-spacing: 0.0158em"
              >against the other. This war at sea expires when the obligation
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5834em; top: 51.8942em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0002em"
              >to keep the peace has expired. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 47.6568em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0459em"
              >Each main Portuguese home city gives the Portuguese player 2 VP
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 48.6068em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0192em"
              >for its control, as indicated on his Player Card. Portuguese
              control &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 3.75em; top: 49.5568em; z-index: 1992"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_144" style="word-spacing: 0.0029em"
              >of all of them is necessary to be eligible for an automatic
              victory. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 50.8442em">
            <span class="stl_10 stl_08 stl_171" style="word-spacing: -0.002em"
              >North African Atlantic Port Control &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 52.0904em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_130" style="word-spacing: -0.0631em"
              >Portugal was in continuous war with the Sultanate of Fez for
              control &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 53.0404em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0548em"
              >of the African cities of the Atlantic coast. </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_80">Anfa</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.04em"
              >, the most important &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 53.9904em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0101em"
              >city in the Atlantic area, awards Portugal 2 VP for its control.
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9168em; top: 53.0944em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.1036em"
              >• Spain and Portugal may not ally as long as the state of war
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5834em; top: 54.0444em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >exists at sea. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9168em; top: 55.2446em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18">•</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9623em; top: 55.2442em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_30" style="word-spacing: -0.0323em"
              >Castile can no longer establish settlements in Ocean &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9583em; top: 56.1942em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_30" style="word-spacing: -0.0462em"
              >Zones 1 and 2, although they can navigate into these &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9583em; top: 57.1442em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_30" style="word-spacing: -0.0386em"
              >zones in order to explore them and pirate there. As a
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 30.9583em; top: 58.0942em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_65" style="word-spacing: -0.009em"
              >reminder, place a “Spain no settlements” </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_30">Alcaçovas &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 7.149em; top: 55.357em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0219em"
              >Each time the mandatory event </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102">P</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_145">ortugal</span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102" style="word-spacing: 0.0223em"
              >, M</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0221em"
              >aster of &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 7.145em; top: 56.307em; z-index: 2238"
          >
            <span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.0218em"
              >the </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_194">A</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.0783em"
              >tlantic </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0687em"
              >is played in the Action Phase, Portugal &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 7.145em; top: 57.257em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.0708em"
              >gets VPs based on the number of African spaces con- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 7.145em; top: 58.207em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_293" style="word-spacing: 0.0691em"
              >trolled from this list: Tangier, Asilah, Mazagan, Anfa,
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.7503em; top: 59.157em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_68" style="word-spacing: 0.0088em"
              >Agadir, Sal</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_99">é</span
