              >Beltranejos: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0438em"
              >The behavior of Beltranejos units changes after the &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.7502em; top: 36.0935em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0139em"
              >Peace of Alcaçovas as follows: &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4168em; top: 37.2937em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_70" style="word-spacing: 0.2437em"
              >• Beltranejos</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.0643em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_70" style="word-spacing: -0.0631em"
              >units on the map may only undertake move, recruit, &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0834em; top: 38.2437em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0161em"
              >and assault actions when the Beltranejos Home card is played
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0834em; top: 39.1937em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0091em"
              >as an event, and this Home card can no longer be used as CPs
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0834em; top: 40.1437em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0597em"
              >(it can however be played to support the Headline Event). This
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0834em; top: 41.0937em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_235" style="word-spacing: -0.0621em"
              >Home card play may be extended with resources and those extra
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0834em; top: 42.0437em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0002em"
              >CPs can also be dedicated to moves for the Beltranejos.
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.2502em; top: 39.6808em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.1249em"
              >Portugal and Spain can still go to war after this time, breaking
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.2502em; top: 40.6308em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_377" style="word-spacing: 0.126em"
              >the Treaty of Tordesillas. Once broken, Spain and Portugal no
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.2502em; top: 41.5808em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0458em"
              >longer have any limitations on where they can found settlements
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.2502em; top: 42.5308em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0114em"
              >and whether or not they can enter the Canary Islands. The cost of
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.2502em; top: 43.4808em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0078em"
              >piracy returns to 2 CP and the cost of declaration of war to 4
              CPs. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4168em; top: 43.2438em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_131" style="word-spacing: 0.232em"
              >• From</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0042em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0011em"
              >this point on, Beltranejos units may perform the assault
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0834em; top: 44.1938em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0511em"
              >action directly upon arrival at a fortified space, without having
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0834em; top: 45.1438em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >to lay siege to it beforehand. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 44.768em">
            <span class="stl_248 stl_08 stl_36">r</span
            ><span class="stl_249 stl_08 stl_164">esis</span
            ><span class="stl_249 stl_08 stl_522">t</span
            ><span class="stl_249 stl_08 stl_18">a</span
            ><span class="stl_249 stl_08 stl_84" style="word-spacing: 0.0784em"
              >NCe of the </span
            ><span class="stl_248 stl_08 stl_36">B</span
            ><span class="stl_249 stl_08 stl_251">e</span
            ><span class="stl_249 stl_08 stl_12">l</span
            ><span class="stl_249 stl_08 stl_225">t</span
            ><span class="stl_249 stl_08 stl_62" style="word-spacing: 0.0873em"
              >raNejos </span
            ><span class="stl_10 stl_08 stl_43">Event &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 46.0142em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_107" style="word-spacing: -0.0632em"
              >This event can occur only if the Beltranejos faction has
              surrendered. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 47.2144em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >When this event is played, the following occurs: &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4168em; top: 46.344em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2319em"
              >• If</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.052em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0571em"
              >the impulse is extended with a resource, the player who con-
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0834em; top: 47.294em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0379em"
              >trols the Beltranejos may repeat an assault action on a single
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0834em; top: 48.244em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0191em"
              >space of those he has assaulted with the play of his home card
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0834em; top: 49.194em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102">J</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0001em"
              >oanna la </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_13">B</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_231" style="word-spacing: 0.0231em"
              >eltraneja </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0002em"
              >in this same impulse. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 48.3314em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_108" style="word-spacing: 0.0986em"
              >• The Beltranejos reappear and gain control of the spaces Tui
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 49.2814em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >and Sanabria (displace (12.5) any units of other powers).
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4168em; top: 50.3942em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.2317em"
              >• The</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.0109em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.016em"
              >Home card </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102">J</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0149em"
              >oanna la </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_13">B</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_231" style="word-spacing: 0.0031em"
              >eltraneja </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0162em"
              >can now be played in &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 50.3985em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_131" style="word-spacing: 0.2321em"
              >• Add</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0051em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_97" style="word-spacing: -0.0015em"
              >one Beltranejos regular in Tui. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0834em; top: 51.3442em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0em"
              >addition to the other two Portuguese Home cards. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 51.5155em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_131" style="word-spacing: 0.2321em"
              >• Add</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0051em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0002em"
              >one Beltranejos regular in Sanabria. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 52.6326em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.2317em"
              >• Create</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0151em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0039em"
              >an additional key that awards VP to Portugal (only) in
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 53.5826em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_89" style="word-spacing: -0.0605em"
              >Tui (indicate this with a square control marker). Control of this
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 54.5326em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0515em"
              >space grants Portugal 1 VP as long as the Beltranejos maintain
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 55.4826em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_100" style="word-spacing: -0.0626em"
              >control. As soon as Tui is controlled by another power, remove
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 56.4326em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_111" style="word-spacing: 0.125em"
              >the square control marker and the space becomes a simple
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 57.3826em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80">space. &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.7502em; top: 52.7106em">
            <span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_304" style="word-spacing: -0.0716em"
              >Breaking The Peace: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_107" style="word-spacing: -0.062em"
              >The Peace o</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_443">f</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_69">A</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_107" style="word-spacing: -0.0622em"
              >lcaçovas is considered broken &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.7502em; top: 53.6606em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >if Portugal and Spain go to war at any time during the Diplomacy
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.7502em; top: 54.6106em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0131em"
              >Phase after the mandatory period of peace has expired or an event
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 3.7502em; top: 55.5606em; z-index: 2328"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_44" style="word-spacing: 0.0249em"
              >puts them at war. </span
            ><span class="stl_342 stl_17 stl_253">(</span
            ><span
              class="stl_340 stl_17 stl_422"
              style="word-spacing: -0.0512em"
              >EXAMPLE: </span
            ><span class="stl_342 stl_17 stl_97" style="word-spacing: 0.017em"
              >If Portugal controls Naples after &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.7494em; top: 56.5106em">
            <span class="stl_342 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.038em"
              >the event </span
            ><span class="stl_362 stl_17 stl_102">D</span
            ><span class="stl_523 stl_17 stl_524" style="word-spacing: 0.0672em"
              >eath of </span
            ><span class="stl_362 stl_17 stl_99">F</span
            ><span class="stl_523 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0372em"
              >errante of </span
            ><span class="stl_362 stl_17 stl_13">N</span
            ><span class="stl_523 stl_17 stl_102">aples</span
            ><span class="stl_342 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0377em"
              >, and decides to keep it, &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.7494em; top: 57.4606em">
            <span class="stl_342 stl_17 stl_108" style="word-spacing: -0.0388em"
              >this will put it at war with Spain, breaking the Peace of
              Alcaçovas, &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 3.7494em; top: 58.4106em; z-index: 2512"
          >
            <span class="stl_342 stl_17 stl_33" style="word-spacing: 0.0646em"
              >if it was in force). </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0532em"
              >If this occurs and the </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_99">T</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13">re</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_190">a</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13">t</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_191" style="word-spacing: 0.0469em"
              >y of </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_154">T</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13">ordesillas &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 3.7494em; top: 59.3606em; z-index: 2562"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.1198em"
              >event has not been played, remove the </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_99">T</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13">re</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_190">a</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13">t</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_191" style="word-spacing: 0.1119em"
              >y of </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_154">T</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13">ordesillas &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 58.4996em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2319em"
              >• Portugal</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0331em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0224em"
              >receives a 1 VP bonus marker for the event to place &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 59.4496em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >on their Player Card. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="page_47" class="stl_ stl_02">
      <div class="stl_03"></div>
      <div class="stl_view">
        <div class="stl_05 stl_06">
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.7667em; top: 1.9227em">
            <span class="stl_16 stl_17 stl_18">48 &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 15.311em; top: 2.1277em">
            <span class="stl_19 stl_17 stl_20">T</span
            ><span class="stl_19 stl_17 stl_18">a</span
            ><span class="stl_19 stl_17 stl_21" style="word-spacing: 0.0021em"
              >nto Monta: The Rise of Ferdinand &amp; Isabella ~ 1470-1516
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 42.001em; top: 2.1269em">
            <span class="stl_22 stl_17 stl_23" style="word-spacing: 0em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 4.3434em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0808em"
              >If this event has been played, Beltranejos units on the map may
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 5.2934em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0169em"
              >only expend CPs for actions from a single resource that is played
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 6.2434em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.0311em"
              >to extend a single Portuguese impulse. These moves must follow
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 7.1935em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0459em"
              >the rules described for Beltranejos under the Peace of Alcaçovas
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 8.1435em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_79" style="word-spacing: -0.0651em"
              >section above. They are additionally limited to only recruiting
              units &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 9.0935em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_526" style="word-spacing: 0.1248em"
              >in the Tui and Sanabria spaces (if they control them). Portugal
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 10.0435em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0281em"
              >may continue to play Combat and Response cards on behalf of the
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 10.9935em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.032em"
              >Beltranejos. Once the Portuguese player has used a resource to
              act &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 11.9435em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0279em"
              >with the units of the Beltranejos resistance, indicate it by
              placing &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 12.8935em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_111" style="word-spacing: 0.125em"
              >the </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_111" style="word-spacing: 0.1185em"
              >Beltranejos Resistance Activated </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_110" style="word-spacing: 0.125em"
              >marker on the Portuguese &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 13.8435em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >Player Card. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 4.3434em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0201em"
              >Between the play of </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_13">I</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0187em"
              >sabella </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102">D</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_102">ies</span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.019em"
              >, C</span
            ><span
              class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_191"
              style="word-spacing: -0.0201em"
              >rown of </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_13">C</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0193em"
              >astile </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_131">S</span
            ><span
              class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_131"
              style="word-spacing: -0.0198em"
              >plit </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80">and &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 5.2934em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0241em"
              >the mandatory event </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_13">C</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0243em"
              >ardinal </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_13">C</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0242em"
              >isneros </span
