            ><span
              class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_173"
              style="word-spacing: -0.0235em"
              >egent </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0241em"
              >(required in the &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 6.2434em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_127" style="word-spacing: 0.0013em"
              >Winter of Turn 6), the following restrictions apply: &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 7.3605em">
