              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0426em"
              >units of Castile and Aragon cannot be part of the same
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 8.3105em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0319em"
              >formation except if they are in the Italian Peninsula or Sicily
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 9.2605em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >and under the command of the </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_33" style="word-spacing: 0.0067em"
              >Great Captain</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_33" style="word-spacing: 0.0067em"
              >. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 10.3775em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2318em"
