            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0679em"
              >fight, retreat and avoid battle just like the other units of that
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 54.4103em">
