          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 55.3603em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >have no impulse or cards of their own). &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 51.6434em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_210" style="word-spacing: -0.0608em"
              >indicated on the space on the Diplomatic Influence Table into
              which &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 52.5934em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_173" style="word-spacing: 0.0219em"
              >the player’s marker is moving. The influence may be allocated to
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 53.5434em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0264em"
              >any power that lists the active power in either an Activate or
              De- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 54.4934em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_97" style="word-spacing: 0.006em"
              >activate line at the bottom of the Diplomatic Influence Table.
              Ad</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_97" style="word-spacing: 0.006em"
              >- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 55.4434em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_173" style="word-spacing: 0.0047em"
              >vance the active player’s influence marker by one level. No
              influ</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_173" style="word-spacing: 0.0047em"
              >- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 56.3934em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0171em"
              >ence may be purchased if a power´s influence marker is already at
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 57.3434em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.041em"
              >level 6. Influence may also not be purchased if the influence
              mark</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.041em"
              >- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 58.2934em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
