              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 56.6717em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.067em"
              >minor power except Navarre or the Papacy (</span
            ><span class="stl_119 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0489em"
