          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 57.6217em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0331em"
              >Muslim player always performs these moves if Rome is under
              &nbsp;</span
            >
