            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_121" style="word-spacing: 0.0809em"
              >Muslim player controls Borgia and all Papal units even
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 21.9105em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_111" style="word-spacing: 0.1249em"
              >though they are not considered to be allied to any Muslim
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 27.5832em; top: 22.8605em; z-index: 3396"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_188">power. &nbsp;</span>
