              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_160" style="word-spacing: -0.0598em"
              >Rome is conquered by the Muslim player, new Popes will
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 27.8607em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0381em"
              >continue to enter the game as normal (the Pope is in exile) and
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 28.8107em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0039em"
              >a Christian player allied to the Papacy does receive the </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_212">P</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_265">a</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_313">p</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_265">a</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_265">l &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 29.7607em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_13">B</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_173" style="word-spacing: 0.0005em"
              >ull </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0em"
              >card at the start of the turn. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.9166em; top: 30.0109em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2319em"
              >• Muslim</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0642em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0588em"
              >units may not attack Papal units or enter Papal-con- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5832em; top: 30.9609em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >trolled spaces. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4166em; top: 30.9609em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.2319em"
              >• If</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.006em"
