            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_162" style="word-spacing: 0.003em"
              >all Papal home spaces are controlled by the Muslim player,
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 31.9109em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0579em"
              >he may move the influence markers as a result of the arrival
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 32.8609em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_115" style="word-spacing: -0.005em"
              >of the new Pope, even if he doesn’t win control of the Papacy
