            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 20.9406em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_225" style="word-spacing: 0.0789em"
              >from the rest of the Aragonese home spaces (consider each
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 21.8906em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_225" style="word-spacing: 0.1em"
              >Aragonese home key as 2 spaces). If a control marker was
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 22.8406em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_217" style="word-spacing: 0.1119em"
              >removed from a space that is not a Catalan home space, it
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 23.7906em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_415" style="word-spacing: -0.0073em"
              >becomes controlled by its home power. If a control marker is
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 24.7406em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_146" style="word-spacing: -0.062em"
              >removed from a Catalan home space—and that space contains
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 25.6906em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_225" style="word-spacing: 0.0589em"
              >no French units—award control of that space to Aragon. If,
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 26.6406em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_110" style="word-spacing: 0.121em"
              >however, a Catalan home space does contain French units,
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 27.5906em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_217" style="word-spacing: -0em"
              >award control of the space to France. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.5321em; top: 16.7311em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_130" style="word-spacing: -0.062em"
              >tory (note that the spaces for these square &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.2497em; top: 17.6811em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0281em"
              >control markers are differentiated on the Player Card and that
              they &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.2497em; top: 18.6311em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.0355em"
              >each award 2 VP for control by their home power—these unique
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.2497em; top: 19.5811em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0642em"
              >square control markers are not usable in other spaces. The exact
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.2497em; top: 20.5311em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0341em"
              >number of keys required by a player for a military victory (and
              the &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.2497em; top: 21.4812em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.1049em"
              >number of home keys each player starts with) are shown in the
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.2497em; top: 22.4312em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0em"
              >table below: &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01 stl_75" style="left: 27.7556em; top: 24.0923em">
            <span class="stl_461 stl_17 stl_80">Player &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.46em; top: 25.2951em">
            <span class="stl_120 stl_17 stl_13">Muslim &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.2803em; top: 26.5103em">
            <span class="stl_120 stl_17 stl_13">Portugal &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.7909em; top: 27.7255em">
            <span class="stl_120 stl_17 stl_13">Spain &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01 stl_75" style="left: 31.0806em; top: 24.0923em">
            <span class="stl_461 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >Home Keys Required</span
            ><span class="stl_461 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.7979em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_461 stl_17 stl_61" style="word-spacing: 0.0059em"
              >Keys for Military Victory &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 32.7563em; top: 25.3078em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0em"
              >3, 4 or 5 * &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 40.1536em; top: 25.3078em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_210" style="word-spacing: 0.0148em"
              >10, 11 or 12 † &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.1939em; top: 26.523em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18">4</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.1939em; top: 27.7382em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18">0</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 34.1939em; top: 28.9534em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18">4</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 41.9911em; top: 26.523em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_637">11 &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 41.9768em; top: 27.7382em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13">15 &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 41.9768em; top: 28.9534em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13">12 &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4166em; top: 28.7908em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.2318em"
              >• Remove</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.0269em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0321em"
              >the Catalan Home card from the game; it is no longer &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 5.0832em; top: 29.7408em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13">used. &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.5709em; top: 28.9407em">
            <span class="stl_120 stl_17 stl_80">France &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 30.3501em">
            <span class="stl_29 stl_17 stl_18">*</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 31.4166em">
            <span class="stl_29 stl_17 stl_18">†</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.2498em; top: 30.3501em">
            <span class="stl_29 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >According to the number of such spaces already in play
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 27.2498em; top: 31.4166em">
            <span class="stl_29 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >According to the number of required spaces in play &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 31.0275em">
            <span class="stl_10 stl_08 stl_60" style="word-spacing: 0.0014em"
              >e Beltranejos Faction &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 3.75em; top: 32.2737em; z-index: 1240"
          >
            <span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_260">T</span
            ><span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_62">e</span
            ><span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_167" style="word-spacing: -0.0707em"
              >mporary Surrender Condition: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_70" style="word-spacing: -0.0631em"
              >If at any time during th</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_638">e</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_42">A</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_70">ction &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 33.2237em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_107" style="word-spacing: -0.0631em"
              >Phase the Beltranejos no longer control any of their home keys,
              they &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 34.1737em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.001em"
              >cease to exist as an active faction. The effects of this
              “temporary” &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 3.75em; top: 35.1237em; z-index: 1432"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_228" style="word-spacing: 0.0057em"
              >surrender are detailed below. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 32.4963em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_97" style="word-spacing: 0.0049em"
              >In order to be eligible for victory, none of these keys may
              contain &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 33.4463em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: -0.0178em"
              >a </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_164" style="word-spacing: -0.0129em"
              >Unrest </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.028em"
              >or </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.028em"
              >Plague </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_97" style="word-spacing: -0.0359em"
              >marker. Automatic military victory is achieved &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 34.3963em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_97" style="word-spacing: 0.0274em"
              >during any Phase of the game. The game ends immediately, even
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 35.3463em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_639" style="word-spacing: -0.0614em"
              >though the turn has not yet reached the Victory Determination
              Phase. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 36.2963em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_70" style="word-spacing: -0.0632em"
              >In the unlikely case that two players each earn an automatic
              military &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 37.2463em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0061em"
              >victory from the same action, award the victory to the player
              with &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 38.1963em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.011em"
              >the most VP at that moment. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 36.4901em">
            <span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_252">T</span
            ><span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_99">e</span
            ><span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_108" style="word-spacing: 0.0781em"
              >mporary Surrender Effects: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.088em"
              >The Portuguese player may not &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 37.4401em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0785em"
              >play cards as CP for Beltranejos units except when he plays the
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 38.3901em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_102">J</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0001em"
              >oanna la </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_13">B</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_231" style="word-spacing: 0.0231em"
              >eltraneja </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0002em"
              >Home card as an event. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 39.7565em">
            <span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.0084em"
              >Regaining Active Status: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0269em"
              >If Beltranejos or Portuguese units (the &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 40.7065em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0341em"
              >latter only if the “Peace of Alcaçovas” has not been signed)
              recap- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 41.6565em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_85" style="word-spacing: 0.0206em"
              >ture a Beltranejos home key, the Beltranejos immediately regains
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 42.6065em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >their active status. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01 stl_75" style="left: 26.25em; top: 39.9331em">
            <span class="stl_76 stl_08 stl_67" style="word-spacing: -0.0054em"
              >22.3 Victory Points by Accumulation &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 41.5129em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.1048em"
              >Because military victories are rare, the game is usually decided
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 26.25em; top: 42.4629em; z-index: 4007"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_144" style="word-spacing: 0.1158em"
              >in the Victory Determination Phase by the accumulation of V</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_194">P</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_194">. &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 26.25em; top: 43.4129em; z-index: 4059"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_121" style="word-spacing: -0.009em"
              >A power’s total VP is the sum of its base, special, and bonus
              V</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_194">P</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_194">. &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 43.9729em">
            <span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_89" style="word-spacing: -0.0725em"
              >Permanent Surrender Condition: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_109" style="word-spacing: -0.0622em"
              >The Beltranejos faction ceases &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 44.9229em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_84" style="word-spacing: -0.0335em"
              >to exist permanently if, during the Victory Determination Phase,
              it &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 45.8729em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.024em"
              >does not control any key or strategic home spaces. It also
              surren- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 3.75em; top: 46.8229em; z-index: 1952"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0052em"
              >ders immediately when the </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_99">T</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13">re</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_190">a</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13">t</span
            ><span
              class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_191"
              style="word-spacing: -0.0101em"
              >y of </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_154">T</span
            ><span class="stl_163 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0002em"
              >ordesillas </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.0001em"
              >event occurs. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 44.7001em">
            <span class="stl_10 stl_08 stl_36" style="word-spacing: -0.015em"
              >Base VP &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 45.9463em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.1053em"
              >Base VPs for all powers are determined by the number of keys
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 46.8963em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0371em"
              >and strategic spaces a player controls that do not contain </span
            ><span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_205" style="word-spacing: -0.0223em"
              >Unrest </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13">or &nbsp;</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 47.8463em">
            <span class="stl_82 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.061em"
              >Plague </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.059em"
              >markers. The base award for each of the strategic spaces
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 26.25em; top: 48.7963em; z-index: 4230"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0136em"
              >is 1 V</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_194">P</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.005em"
              >. </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_102">K</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0106em"
              >ey spaces award 1 VP except for home space of France,
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 49.7463em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0489em"
              >the North African Alliance, and Portugal; these keys award their
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 50.6963em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_111" style="word-spacing: 0.1188em"
              >respective home powers 2 VP each when controlled. Note that
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 51.6463em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0137em"
              >these same keys only award 1 VP when they are not controlled by
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 26.25em; top: 52.5963em; z-index: 4445"
          >
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_140" style="word-spacing: 0.0091em"
              >their home power. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 48.1894em">
            <span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_108" style="word-spacing: 0.0106em"
              >Permanent Surrender Effects: </span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0329em"
              >Apply these effects upon perma</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0329em"
              >- &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 49.1393em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.0001em"
              >nent surrender: &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4166em; top: 50.3395em">
            <span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.2318em"
              >• Remove</span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0051em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_78 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0em"
              >the Beltranejos´ Home card from the game. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 4.4166em; top: 51.5397em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.2318em"
              >• Remove</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_18" style="word-spacing: 0.0051em"
              >&nbsp;</span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0001em"
              >all of the Beltranejos leaders from the game. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
