          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 23.9435em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0em"
              >the victory phase. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 24.5167em">
            <span class="stl_10 stl_08 stl_435" style="word-spacing: -0.0229em"
              >Time Limit Victory &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 25.2268em">
            <span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_88" style="word-spacing: 0.0373em"
              >Catalan-Controlled Spaces Upon Surrender: </span
            ><span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: 0.036em"
              >For every two or &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 26.1768em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_108" style="word-spacing: 0.0307em"
              >three spaces with Catalan control markers upon surrender, gain 1
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 3.75em; top: 27.1268em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_13" style="word-spacing: -0.0371em"
              >VP (22.1). &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 25.7629em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_162" style="word-spacing: 0.0639em"
              >If no player has won by the end of Turn 7, award the win to the
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 26.7129em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0532em"
              >player with the highest VP total at that time. If two or more
              players &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 27.6629em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: -0.0621em"
              >tie for highest total, the player with the highest total in the
              previous &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 28.6129em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_84" style="word-spacing: 0.0074em"
              >turn is declared the winner. If the players were tied on that
              earlier &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 29.5629em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_80" style="word-spacing: 0.0449em"
              >turn, proceed backward one turn at a time until the tie is
              broken. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 30.5129em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_201" style="word-spacing: -0.0389em"
              >A Time Limit Victory can only occur in the Victory Determination
              &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="stl_01" style="left: 26.25em; top: 31.4629em">
            <span class="stl_81 stl_17 stl_126" style="word-spacing: 0.002em"
              >Phase at the end of Turn 7. &nbsp;</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="stl_01"
            style="left: 3.75em; top: 28.4101em; z-index: 978"
          >
            <span class="stl_91 stl_17 stl_45" style="word-spacing: 0.0019em"
